<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Aug1939"><font color="red">15 August 1939</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Also please send me Vol I of <i>Phineas Finn</i> which is on top of the bookshelves &hellip; Now for L.G. There are 4 versions of ALP, Navire d&apos;Argent, edition de luxe with preface by Colum, Faber and Faber pamphlet and the final &hellip; I don&apos;t think there is much difference between 2 and 3. </div>
